Bloodline
by Eli Brody

In "Bloodline", you assume control over a small developing population. How will your creatures be mutated? What will they evolve into?

This is my entry for the 24th Ludum Dare 48-hour solo game development challenge.

Visit my blog at http://blog.megastructure.org/

